ðŸŸ¢ Dual Ultrasonic Sensor (HC-SR04) with Raspberry Pi 5

  This project demonstrates how to connect two HC-SR04 ultrasonic distance sensors to a Raspberry Pi 5, read distance measurements quickly and reliably, and avoid common issues such as false long-distance readings and GPIO damage.

  The project is suitable for beginners and can be extended to applications such as parking systems, obstacle detection, safety systems, and IoT projects.

