âš ï¸ Important:
  Raspberry Pi GPIO pins operate at 3.3V, while the HC-SR04 Echo pin outputs 5V.
  A voltage divider is mandatory to protect the Raspberry Pi.

âš¡ Power Connections

Both ultrasonic sensors share the same power rails.

