ðŸ“Œ GPIO Pin Assignment
  Ultrasonic Sensor 1
  Function	GPIO (BCM)	Physical Pin
  TRIG1	GPIO 23	Pin 16
  ECHO1	GPIO 24	Pin 18 (via voltage divider)
  Ultrasonic Sensor 2
  Function	GPIO (BCM)	Physical Pin
  TRIG2	GPIO 17	Pin 11
  ECHO2	GPIO 27	Pin 13 (via voltage divider)

